cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.GR, cs.AI, cs.LG

The paper proposes a model that generates 3D house models from natural language descriptions, which involves tasks such as language processing, image synthesis, and layout prediction. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Additionally, the paper also involves natural language processing, which suggests it could also belong to cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also deals with layout prediction and graph representation, which could fall under cs.GR (Graphics). The use of generative models and neural networks suggests it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
